{"tid":1825893,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗區議員辦事處外 整幅連儂牆被清","createTime":"2020-01-15T16:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T14:58:25.000Z","uid":35658,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"54beee84d254abbe3ecfe14cb9c2ce5678255045","tid":1825893,"uid":35658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T16:32:17.000Z","msg":"深水埗區議員甄啟榮 之前幾屆做騎牆派 <br />\n以前民協後來跟老鼠芬 後來比建制派人黎搶<br />\n今屆話自己黃保住左個位<br />\n<br />\n今晚佢辦事處外牆整幅連儂牆比人清左<br />\n清既係一個阿叔 齊工具有埋梯<br />\n當時辦事處中門大開有職員在內<br />\n同一牆上佢自己既議員post 沒有被移除<br />\n<br />\n佢自己辦事處門上都仲貼住張光復香港文宣既<br />\n即管睇下佢會唔會自己撕<br />\n<br />\n如果果個阿叔係佢d人 咁依d偽黃真係養唔熟"},{"pid":"1bc54dad9d751561c4c152910543e4dda1390e1d","tid":1825893,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:05:04.000Z","msg":"咁奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2743700177340b91eda6300ea4d6131d37266f32","tid":1825893,"uid":92038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:38:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd465b5e5688c44c5dd0c67eeaa72cd306a3d05f","tid":1825893,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T18:09:08.000Z","msg":"請密切監察呢d食血饅頭上位既議員！"},{"pid":"8e764e8981a7a6be795a29ba06ccef66f65a07d8","tid":1825893,"uid":207481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T20:15:25.000Z","msg":"推 要密切留意"},{"pid":"aceb3dc028b1ab8b5ce93c7a02429c4c85febfb6","tid":1825893,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T20:44:05.000Z","msg":"會唔會清潔再update?"},{"pid":"40a19b5621bccc21f8b05d520e50c2d4bc5b4916","tid":1825893,"uid":35658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T02:26:43.000Z","msg":"會繼續留意<br />\n今朝睇仍然清晒"},{"pid":"04039413053da7b7a757bd1729c2d662bb0b7d01","tid":1825893,"uid":35658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"今日一幅牆變左幾張大型揮春 有光復口號<br />\n另一幅牆補貼左少少舊文宣 <br />\n唔見新文宣 未知係唔係區議員既人